categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: This unidentified male Kajain'sa'Nikto was a member of the Ohnaka Gang during the Clone Wars. He resided in their base on Florrum. This Nikto was present in 22 BBY when the gang captured Count Dooku, attracting the attention of the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker. The Nikto drank from a cup till he toppled from his chair, nearly knocking over Piit, a Weequay pirate. He was one of the few members of the gang who was not a Weequay; other known pirates who were not Weequay are an Ishi Tib and several other Nikto, as well as Bith and Jawas.
